content.title: LearnWithQ3 2024 Budget Update
content.visibleText:
Q3 Plans
1. We plan to shift part of our theory toward user acquisition and monetization. Key to this strategy is selling on par with the value our steep user acquisition funnel with targeted landing pages and supporting research. We will build out proof points of program effectiveness both to validate the core strategy and to compel partners to make subsequent purchases.
2. Drive proven epidemic... (text continues)

TeachTales
We are building a reading app whose mission is to help users 'read what they love to love to read.' Using AI, we want to make 'reading what you love' possible like never before.

Q2 Progress
In Q2, we've shipped an MVP, and we have started acquiring users through paid ads over the past few weeks.
The apps provides personalized and engaging stories to users, aligned with their reading level. The user answers questions, personalized to their understanding of the text and enabling to guide their reading journey.
